snippet: Both lost on the road to unranked teams: Oklahoma was surprised by Kansas State, and North Carolina was upset by Notre Dame.
abstract: College Basketball Roundup; Kansas State men's team defeats Oklahoma, 80-69; other men's and women's scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Both lost on the road to unranked teams: Oklahoma was surprised by Kansas State, and North Carolina was upset by Notre Dame.
